1<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to STING - Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
            color: #f1f5f9;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .email-content {
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 
                0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .brand-name {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fbbf24;
            margin: 16px 0 8px 0;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }
        
        .tagline {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #10b981;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #f1f5f9;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #e2e8f0;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .code-container {
            background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid #fbbf24;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .code-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #fbbf24;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .registration-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fbbf24;
            font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, 'Cascadia Code', 'Roboto Mono', Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;
            letter-spacing: 0.3em;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            user-select: all;
            -webkit-user-select: all;
            -moz-user-select: all;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .copy-hint {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        
        .welcome-benefits {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .benefits-title {
            color: #10b981;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .benefit-item {
            color: #a7f3d0;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .benefit-icon {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        
        .expiry-info {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .expiry-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #93c5fd;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 32px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.3);
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .help-link {
            color: #fbbf24;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .help-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        /* Mobile responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .email-content {
                padding: 20px 16px;
            }
            
            .glass-card {
                padding: 24px 20px;
            }
            
            .registration-code {
                font-size: 28px;
                letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            }
            
            .brand-name {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .welcome-message {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-content">
            <div class="glass-card">
                <div class="header">
                    <div class="brand-name">STING</div>
                    <p class="tagline">Secure Intelligence & Analytics Platform</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="welcome-message">
                    üéâ Welcome to STING!
                </div>
                
                <div class="greeting">
                    Hi{{if .Identity.traits.name.first}} {{.Identity.traits.name.first}}{{else if .Identity.traits.email}} {{.Identity.traits.email}}{{end}},
                </div>
                
                <div class="message">
                    Thank you for joining STING! Please verify your email address to complete your registration and access your account.
                </div>
                
                <div class="code-container">
                    <div class="code-label">Your Verification Code</div>
                    <div class="registration-code">{{.RegistrationCode}}</div>
                    <div class="copy-hint">üëÜ Tap to select and copy</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="expiry-info">
                    <p class="expiry-text">
                        ‚è∞ This code will expire in <strong>15 minutes</strong> for security reasons.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="welcome-benefits">
                    <div class="benefits-title">What you can do with STING:</div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <span class="benefit-icon">ü§ñ</span>
                        Access advanced AI-powered analytics
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <span class="benefit-icon">üîê</span>
                        Secure, passwordless authentication
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <span class="benefit-icon">üìä</span>
                        Real-time intelligence dashboards
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit-item">
                        <span class="benefit-icon">‚ö°</span>
                        Lightning-fast processing
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="message">
                    Once verified, you'll be able to set up additional security features like passkeys and two-factor authentication.
                </div>
                
                <div class="footer">
                    <p class="footer-text">
                        Welcome to the future of secure intelligence! 
                        <a href="#" class="help-link">Need help getting started?</a>
                    </p>
                    <p class="footer-text">
                        STING - Secure Intelligence & Analytics Platform
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>